  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5aa0fb32-f0df-4a14-b727-686a8198ac2b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b6fc85e2-a436-465b-876b-4d6aa6cec7ae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82b52744-a38d-4aa6-b297-19a897ae4680\"><b>안녕하세요, </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6a4fe868-79ef-4f01-a89f-93cb3de75ae3\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2877fba-c390-4052-a7dd-252ff1366eb3\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5aa0fb32-f0df-4a14-b727-686a8198ac2b\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7053dc93-642e-49ba-abe3-f9a98a02ac03\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"7\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_7.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bcdf4553-8fad-449b-b47f-d1ccbcbf64e5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-88206c56-abb5-45d9-ba19-4ceee7fa4a85\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6e63e274-a52c-40c2-bc92-11f8c27c9145\">다이어트를 결심했지만, 굶거나 힘든 운동은 피하고 싶으신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8fc11fac-8e30-4e1d-b6e9-6cd35d0c5985\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e0b597f2-d80e-4454-a9fd-93a17b89d602\">무리한 식단 조절이나 과도한 운동은 금방 지치게 만들고, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b6f1218d-4c35-4c75-9f71-fde010002bc2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0277762b-aa05-4692-9e3d-cb70044de825\">요요 현상을 부르기 쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b906d0e0-0515-4ff8-828c-4edd2f56be4b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29718606-d13f-41ff-aa5f-cc8d966df588\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20c84472-e176-447c-9332-56cdd1040e57\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-25c7796c-316f-44e5-8b06-267a7afd4742\"><b>기혈 순환을 촉진해 살이 잘 빠지는 몸으로 만드는 한의학적 다이어트 방법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdb02ffe-41f0-4951-8d2f-3c7de2022822\">을 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3a1d5ea-7dea-4c24-9ebe-405f5c79a64b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-41e06bae-b240-4292-9b63-7e4526561cfe\">알려드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-bcdf4553-8fad-449b-b47f-d1ccbcbf64e5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-50100040-006e-40b7-8f04-2df59cf8b289\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3065c8bd-8a6d-42e6-b16c-a307e56c81f9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3065c8bd-8a6d-42e6-b16c-a307e56c81f9\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ec95fb1929f6a907.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1400\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1400\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ec95fb1929f6a907.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ec95fb1929f6a907.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-3065c8bd-8a6d-42e6-b16c-a307e56c81f9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cad68d4-d7b6-4ef2-ac8a-c7027a5f317b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4e23aef0-f07a-4e6b-b0a3-0c59a238f351\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d5430cbd-91e3-42dd-b6ef-77b235904246\"><b>기혈 순환이 원활해야 살이 빠집니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79e57b9a-88a1-4cd0-be02-58182f46018a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d694c49-d702-47d5-af46-b622de3eb390\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-38fbf55d-959e-4782-b6d7-f6961c764fb1\"><b>1. 왜 기혈 순환이 중요한가요?</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae241a0f-c9cc-4c13-9d91-f9210b1d1993\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f1664dc-6871-4409-8062-b2b38f257ee9\">한의학에서는 ‘살이 잘 안 빠진다’는 것을 단순히 칼로리 문제로 보지 않습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-37f9b267-055b-4a83-bdaf-c73e11c102a3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39c54507-b25a-4a80-a585-23e87cad8a06\"><b>기(氣)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f612e2e2-3488-402b-80fc-9f8b1bb201bb\">: 몸에 에너지를 공급하는 힘입니다. 기가 약하거나 흐름이 막히면 대사가 떨어집니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42a196d5-ffde-4baf-84c6-f3c0e641a793\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bdb5e880-60fb-43f2-b01f-7f25968c7e82\"><b>혈(血)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fab58013-d79b-462f-90ee-01f3dd9f5221\">: 영양과 산소를 온몸에 전달하는 혈액입니다. 혈이 잘 돌지 않으면 노폐물과 수분이 쌓여 부종과 체중 증가로 이어집니다.</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1298b590-f88d-42e2-b6bc-feffa8b442f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-46ac39fd-3ea8-4fed-99da-987272d602d1\">즉, 기와 혈이 원활히 순환해야 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ccaa5a3-dce4-49aa-b5e5-f6b6237b561f\"><b>에너지 소모가 활발해지고 지방이 잘 분해</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4e9f23fa-4f8b-462f-8d34-6a304e7b44ad\">됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-79e57b9a-88a1-4cd0-be02-58182f46018a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-f9cd6b4b-24e1-4024-99e6-c19e481728c6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca936c24-2c9f-4620-9e0d-090261b55919\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-712e5419-2cc9-49db-acc0-91c6fc269ebf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0b53e885-9dd6-4bb7-a77a-1460fa4bf51f\"><b>2. 기혈 순환을 돕는 간단한 방법</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2a2a222-0217-4647-93b5-e0b55227de5d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e33788c-0dd7-4b73-93b5-c86f1d93582f\"><b>하루 20~30분 빠르게 걷기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c072f575-bc4f-49e6-86ce-7e00e39e9fdb\">: 하체 근육이 움직이면 혈액이 심장과 뇌까지 원활히 올라갑니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8f13be9e-6435-4fba-bd7c-bd679cd5d50e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f920927-1b75-44c4-a7d7-8f4bf38d955b\"><b>전신 스트레칭</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc967ea8-2f2d-4b9a-985e-2e7be14bb26e\">: 목, 어깨, 허리, 발목을 부드럽게 풀어주면 기와 혈이 골고루 돌게 됩니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a724758-6b19-47a7-a6b8-9d03e8fb9cbe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b4d4af51-4b06-4876-9d6c-99ad3d92dbe6\"><b>따뜻한 물 자주 마시기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f27c643b-ddfe-4fc8-8df7-3c79701383ee\">: 혈관이 수축되지 않도록 하고, 노폐물 배출을 돕습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-28eda623-c5fe-40e6-89fe-1e6ae2dc3e4f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-261c618f-9d52-44f3-981f-7d8b8eb2c60e\"><b>심호흡</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-432823a0-7d1d-4751-9188-0d8b0cefeaa6\">: 깊게 숨을 들이마시고 천천히 내쉬면 기 순환이 안정되고 대사가 활발해집니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-ca936c24-2c9f-4620-9e0d-090261b55919\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-291563c9-2854-4ba8-98fb-2b536d7d5dcf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-155191d6-a14b-49a0-8338-536e57062826\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c017cc0f-d403-4192-ba40-bc4847ee37a8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3fe014fb-90c9-4c7d-b09e-9d68ebf43de9\"><b>3. 굶지 않아도 되는 건강한 식습관</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e4a1b0a-b052-49d7-a5f4-c65f85355839\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dbeb2f24-89c3-4430-a0d3-b2b27c4ffa44\">무조건 굶는 다이어트는 근육 손실과 기초대사량 감소로 이어져, 오히려 살이 잘 찌는 체질을 만듭니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-065c2aa8-ff5c-47e4-8a24-aaaaa0edffcd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c623988a-f221-483c-bdec-a947383220c8\"><b>단백질 충분히 섭취</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dab2b52a-7a1b-4359-9edf-f43a4ff71eb0\">: 살코기, 두부, 달걀, 콩류 등</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-99f849c1-5cfc-4962-b5a7-d0abf529d93d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d22cb6f3-65e9-44f7-931d-f96aab06dba6\"><b>가공식품과 당분 줄이기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc54ed79-16fa-4ae5-ac0b-d7d3ab360240\">: 혈당이 급격히 오르면 지방 축적이 빨라집니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1a91a10d-4335-4a25-9e37-d1560a059322\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8675e586-4de4-4dc0-9d23-a73615f2140a\"><b>채소와 해조류 자주 먹기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7340057e-3a78-4629-9bdf-2825824ebc5a\">: 포만감을 주면서도 칼로리는 낮습니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-155191d6-a14b-49a0-8338-536e57062826\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-7dbac38b-636f-495d-ac7f-53306f13765d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab825f75-8e33-4142-8e59-376998a89758\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e2cda44-ef2e-43c7-aaae-235c6db6e207\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5a85553d-c421-4190-994b-9700513f6d63\"><b>4. 요요 없는 다이어트를 위한 생활 관리</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-29ad1e5b-e55c-44f9-99e5-e4a1070eea96\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d1b6c20b-3432-4eb8-8e74-73a3f4c492ca\">충분한 수면으로 호르몬 균형 유지</span></p></li><li class=\"s